of Diocesan schools Some 28000 students will be gin classes next Wednesday and Thursday September 34 Mon signor Applegate said Elementary schools will begin classes on Wednesday with most of the high schools opening their doors on Thursday An exception will be the new Bishop Hartley High School Livingston Ave and Zettler Rd which will begin classes on Wednesday Sept 11 at 930 am for the seventh and eighth grade students enrolled there with the ninth grade or fresh man class reporting the follow ing day September 12 also at 930 am This delay is necessary in order to ready the recently finished classrooms according to Monsig nor Edward Spiers acting princi pal of Hartley Ten new principals will greet pupils in Diocesan schools next week according to a report is sued from the school office"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-09-04T23:14:09.101Z", "group": ["ndnp/ohi", "ohio-historical-society-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83007243/1957-08-30/ed-1/?sp=1", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_amaryllis_ver01:data:sn83007243:00414210247:1957083001:0089/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=282&w=202", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_amaryllis_ver01:data:sn83007243:00414210247:1957083001:0089/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=565&w=405", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_amaryllis_ver01:data:sn83007243:00414210247:1957083001:0089/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1130&w=810", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/ohi/batch_ohi_amaryllis_ver01/data/sn83007243/00414210247/1957083001/0089.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 1, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "ohio", "franklin", "columbus"], "location_city": ["columbus"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["franklin"], "location_state": ["ohio"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/p